<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Fruit Flashcards 4x3 - English & Malayalam (Emoji)</title>
  <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link
    href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    rel="stylesheet"
  />
  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+Malayalam:wght@400;600&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet"
  />

  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 30px 15px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .flashcards-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 25px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto 50px auto;
    }

    @media (max-width: 992px) {
      .flashcards-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .flashcards-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .flashcard {
      perspective: 1000px;
      cursor: pointer;
      height: 320px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      position: relative;
    }

    .flashcard-inner {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border-radius: 20px;
      transition: transform 0.6s ease-in-out;
      transform-style: preserve-3d;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      background: white;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .flashcard.flipped .flashcard-inner {
      transform: rotateY(180deg);
    }

    .card-front,
    .card-back {
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border-radius: 20px;
      backface-visibility: hidden;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      user-select: none;
    }

    .card-front {
      background: #fff;
      color: #333;
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 10px #ddd;
    }

    .card-back {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4facfe, #00f2fe);
      color: white;
      transform: rotateY(180deg);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-family: "Noto Sans Malayalam", sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .fruit-emoji {
      font-size: 140px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      user-select: none;
    }

    .fruit-name-english {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1.2px;
      user-select: none;
    }

    .flip-hint {
      position: absolute;
      top: 12px;
      right: 12px;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
      color: white;
      padding: 5px 12px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.3s;
      user-select: none;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .flashcard:hover .flip-hint {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    /* Reset button styling */
    .reset-btn {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ff6b6b, #ee5a52);
      border: none;
      color: white;
      padding: 14px 36px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(238, 90, 82, 0.4);
    }

    .reset-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ee5a52, #ff6b6b);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.6);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üçé Fruit Flashcards ü•≠</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">
        Learn fruit names in English & Malayalam | ‡¥á‡¥Ç‡¥ó‡µç‡¥≤‡µÄ‡¥∑‡¥ø‡¥≤‡µÅ‡¥Ç ‡¥Æ‡¥≤‡¥Ø‡¥æ‡¥≥‡¥§‡µç‡¥§‡¥ø‡¥≤‡µÅ‡¥Ç ‡¥™‡¥¥‡¥ô‡µç‡¥ô‡¥≥‡µÅ‡¥ü‡µÜ ‡¥™‡µá‡¥∞‡µÅ‡¥ï‡µæ ‡¥™‡¥†‡¥ø‡¥ï‡µç‡¥ï‡µÅ‡¥ï
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flashcards-grid" id="flashcardsGrid">
      <!-- Flashcards inserted by JS -->
